%% Diagram: Tag-based purge — origin tags responses; one purge invalidates all URLs that share the tag
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Origin
    participant CDN
    participant Idx as Tag index

    Note over Origin,Idx: Cache fill with tagged responses
    CDN->>Origin: GET /products/123
    Origin-->>CDN: 200 + Surrogate-Key: p-123 cat-elec
    CDN->>Idx: bind tags → /products/123

    CDN->>Origin: GET /categories/electronics
    Origin-->>CDN: 200 + Surrogate-Key: cat-elec p-123
    CDN->>Idx: bind tags → /categories/electronics

    Note over Origin,Idx: Tag purge fans out to bound URLs
    Origin->>CDN: POST /purge tag=p-123
    CDN->>Idx: lookup p-123
    Idx-->>CDN: /products/123, /categories/electronics
    Note over CDN: invalidate both
